But if you want to support me with a coin, then you can do it here.

1. easynegative

PLEASE CHECK YOUR LORA NAME AFTER DOWNLOAD.

Or you can add same tags to the negative prompt for any other outfit you want.

Also you may improve it with prompt: athletic

Enjoy and share your feedback.
